===Format===
* '''Creators Unite: Rondo Rampage''' : ''April 18th - 19th
** 16 teams.
** 2 matchdays.
** All match played in Rondo Map.
* '''Day 1''' : ''April 18th
** Match 1: All Weapons
** Match 2: Face Off One
*** WOW mode 3v3
*** 16th team of match 1 vs anyone from top 4 team of match 1.
** Match 3: Vehicle & Pistol Only
** Match 4: Melee Only

* '''Day 2''' : ''April 19th
** Match 1: All Weapons
** Match 2: Snipers Only
** Match 3: Face Off Two
*** WOW Mode DBS 3v3
*** 16th team from overall standing vs anyone from top 4 team from overall standing.
** Match 4: Shotgun Only
** Match 5: Melee Only

